                    </div>
                    <span>This book uses any Group Policy knowledge you may think you already have and expands it by 1000% (technically impossible I know but you get my drift!). It's a pleasure to read and the author's knowledge and devotion to the subject come shining through. If you need to design or support Group Policies then you must buy this book.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Awesome Book! A MUST Have!</div>
